snippet.title: Outbreak Island - Official 'Roman' Teaser Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
Watch the eerie new trailer for Outbreak Island, an open-world sandbox survival horror game. As a detective it’s up to you to investigate the strange events unfolding on a mysterious island, using a camera and handcrafted weapons to survive. Build and fortify your base and improve your hunting and farming skills as you embark on a dangerous journey. 

Outbreak Island will be released in 2023.
